[ti: Petals in the Mist]
[length: 03:52.040]

[00:16.405]Spring rain falls into the night.
[00:20.086]The distant lights slowly come into view.

[00:25.605]The day I bought my train ticket.
[00:29.018]Spring rain fell from the sky.
[00:32.935]The city you once spoke of.
[00:35.725]Suddenly feels closer and closer.
[00:40.060]Platform lights softly glow.
[00:43.198]The train heads toward the misty land.
[00:47.398]My luggage carries so many unspoken words.
[00:50.146]And memories of your face.

[00:54.668]The misty rain falls outside the window.
[00:58.238]Like the stories you told long ago.
[01:01.820]After all these years.
[01:05.884]I still haven't forgotten.

[01:09.668]Petals drifting through the misty rain.
[01:12.869]Floating toward Suzhou.
[01:16.229]I slowly follow the wind.
[01:20.298]Chasing the fragrance of flowers.
[01:23.685]If reunion takes too long.
[01:26.829]If every story must end.
[01:31.120]At least I can see with my own eyes.
[01:34.739]The spring scenery you once described.

[01:52.838]The city slowly fades behind me.
[01:55.873]Dawn gradually draws near.
[01:59.881]Rivers pass through unfamiliar lands.
[02:03.257]Carrying the outline of spring.
[02:06.820]When I open old photographs.
[02:10.439]You are still standing in the frame.
[02:14.098]And at last I am heading toward.
[02:18.233]The land of my longing.

[02:21.797]If meeting again is only a luxury.
[02:25.340]I still want to walk to the very end.
[02:29.061]Even if you've already left.
[02:32.612]The spring breeze still remains there.

[02:36.542]Petals drifting through the misty rain.
[02:40.132]Floating toward Suzhou.
[02:43.215]I slowly follow the wind.
[02:47.267]Chasing the fragrance of flowers.
[02:50.350]Even if you're no longer by my side.
[02:53.939]I still want to look toward the distance.
[02:58.197]Some longings truly.
[03:01.901]Can carry a person far away.

[03:05.137]The wind carries the fragrance southward.
[03:08.647]The rain writes longing into endless lines.
[03:12.194]I pack all the dreams of these years.
[03:16.304]Into my luggage.
[03:19.547]Daybreak is near.
[03:22.516]The station announcement softly sounds.
[03:27.135]Next stop.
[03:30.255]Suzhou Station.